age=EN>Lybernia Belisama</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.sherilyn.net/pendulum/icon.jpg BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(4/6/01 5:23:22 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://home.columbus.rr.com/sherilyn70/lybernia4a.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: equipment advice needed</span><hr size=1> Since you didn't say how much money you have it's hard to say. <br>
Feet : Wolf fur slippers with +20 mana for around 800p or Cyrstal lined slippers with +3 wis for around 2k.  <br>
Belt : Crystalline belt with +3 wis and +10 hp, or crystalline silk belt with +3 wis and +20 mana.  Probably around 1k for either.  <br>
Back : Molten Cloak or Mamorth hide Cloak, both with +4 wis for about 2k.  There is also the Kunzar cloak with +2 wis for about 400p <br>
<br>
These three slots are harder to fill since there are very few items in the middle range to put in them.   <p><img src=http://home.columbus.rr.com/sherilyn70/lybernia.GIF><BR>
